led microgrids, smart solar street lights, real-time remote monitoring and analytics, and rooftop, ground-mounted and institutional projects; wind farm SCADA and monitoring; transmission solutions, comprising EHV cables, substation automation, SCADA integration, and smart communication infrastructure; and feeder automation, unmanned substations, energy monitoring, and smart communication infrastructure. In addition, the company is involved in the provision of engineering services; design, procurement, and execution of EPC project; manufacture of protection, control, and power distribution panels; SCADA and automation integration; and EPC and integration services for solar power, hybrid systems, and EV-ready infrastructure. Further, it engages in management consultancy and project execution services businesses; and trade of electrical items, which includes LED lights and other related products and components. Sharika Enterprises Limited was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Noida, India."}}